title: 480X800 Comic Book Wallpapers
description:
I have recently upgraded my phone and no longer need the nearly 1400 wallpapers I made for my old phone. These have already been posted on Zedge, so some of you may have seen some of these before but I felt that, before I delete them, I should put them out there, all in one place, incase anyone else might like them.
I am also going to put out there my 960X800 collection.
These are mostly Marvel related but there is some other stuff mixed in and it is mostly sexy superhero chicks.

Enjoy.
